So video feed cutting out is a super common problem with fpv drone flying
But what about just generating a map from the camera data plus some map elevation data
And defaulting to that when you lose video
Ofc signal all the alarms too

instruction:
Thomas Evers: Okay
Sorrry
Chaos
I'm in train
Campus to rotterdam
10 min train
Something crashes and there are a bunch of trains waiting
We staan stil op Schiedam voor 10 min, onzeker hoe lang nog
Ik heb nog 45 min om op rot centraal te komen
So
I get out and run to the tram
And I take the tram
En ik moet overstappen op "de beurs"
Ik kom aan bij een station, en terwijl we stil staan veranderd het digitale bord in de trein ineens naar volgende station "de beurs"
Dus ik, shit
Ga snel naar de deur opening
De deur gaat dicht
Opeens herinnerd een andere guy ook, ik moet er ook uit
Ik hou de deur nog net open zodat ik er door kan en daarna hij
Maar ik vraag aan hen
Hem
Is dit de beurs
Hij natuurlijk, jajaja! Zeggen
Ik ga er uit
Hij, zegt, oh nee toch niet, sorry....
En loopt weg
Ik heb op dat moment nog 12 min om op centraal te komen
Er gaan geen trams voor 10 min and even if they did,I'd be 10 min late
So it would have left
So I run outside to get a go scooter. Look at where centrum is
Go scooter, back wheel broken and wobling super much, as if it was completely loose
I consider just driving it for 2 km
But think it's not worth avoiding paying 40 bux and leaving a day later
So I try take another scooter
I have 8 or 9 min at this point
I drive to the station, but have to keep stopping to look at where I need to be exactly
I am hella stessing
I make it to the station and decide to ditch the scooter (legally) and make a run for it, it's somewhere close
I ask a guy, he tells me, other side
I sprint
I see the place, and re ognise it, because that's where we got on the bus to slovenia
I can feel victory
Both being on time, and yet having spent no time waiting. perfect harmony and efficiency.
I run, and just as I get to the end of the busses, doubting if I had gone too far, or god forbid, I was too late, the flixbus came driving around the corner. As I squinted my eyes to see if it was actually, my bus, I felt my body relaxing and confirming sensation come over me.
